<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>무한의 탑</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css?v=<%= version %>">
    <link href="https://cdn.quilljs.com/1.3.6/quill.snow.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.quilljs.com/1.3.6/quill.js"></script>
    <script>
      if (/Mobi|Android/i.test(navigator.userAgent)) {
        document.documentElement.classList.add('is-mobile');
      }
    </script>
</head>
<body>

<div id="abyssal-shop-modal" class="modal-overlay" style="display: none;">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <span class="close-button">&times;</span>
        <h2>🌌 심연의 상점</h2>
        <p class="inventory-tip" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
            보유 중인 심연의 파편: <span id="abyssal-shard-count" style="color: var(--primal-color); font-weight: bold;">0</span>개
        </p>
        <div id="abyssal-shop-grid" class="inventory-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(150px, 1fr));">
            </div>
    </div>
</div>

    <div id="auth-container">
        <div class="auth-box">
            <h1 id="auth-title">로그인</h1>
            <form id="auth-form">
                <input type="text" id="username" placeholder="아이디" required autocomplete="username">
                <input type="password" id="password" placeholder="비밀번호" required autocomplete="current-password">
                <p id="auth-message"></p>
                <button type="submit" id="submit-button">로그인</button>
            </form>
            <p id="toggle-auth">계정이 없으신가요? <span id="toggle-link">회원가입</span></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="kakao-register-container" style="display: none;">
        <div class="auth-box">
            <h1>새 계정 정보 입력</h1>
            <form id="kakao-register-form">
                <p>카카오 인증이 완료되었습니다. 사용할 닉네임과 비밀번호를 입력해주세요.</p>
                <input type="text" id="kakao-reg-username" placeholder="새 닉네임" required>
                <input type="password" id="kakao-reg-password" placeholder="비밀번호" required>
                <p id="kakao-reg-message"></p>
                <button type="submit">가입 완료</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="kakao-link-container" style="display: none;">
        <div class="auth-box">
            <h1>닉네임 변경</h1>
            <form id="kakao-link-form">
                <p>카카오 인증이 완료되었습니다. 앞으로 사용할 새로운 닉네임을 입력해주세요.</p>
                <input type="text" id="kakao-link-username" placeholder="새 닉네임" required>
                <p id="kakao-link-message"></p>
                <button type="submit">변경 완료</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="game-app-container" style="display: none;">
        <div id="announcement-banner"></div>

        <div class="top-bar">
           <div id="user-info">
                <span id="fame-icon"></span>
                <span id="fame-score-display" style="margin-left: 2px;"></span>
                <span id="welcome-username" style="margin-left: 8px;"></span>님 환영합니다!
            </div>
            <div class="top-buttons">
                <button id="ranking-button">🏆 랭킹</button>
                <button id="loot-record-button">💎 득템</button>
                <button id="enhancement-record-button">✨ 강화</button>
                <button id="online-users-button">👥 접속자</button>
                <button id="mailbox-button">📬 우편함</button>
                <a href="https://discord.gg/zxkdFPkZVt" target="_blank" id="discord-button">💬 디스코드</a>
                <button id="codex-button">📖 도감</button>
<button id="title-codex-button">📜 칭호</button>
<button id="auto-sell-button">🤖 자판기</button>
<button id="abyssal-shop-button" style="background-color: #6a0dad; color: white;">🌌 심연</button>
            </div>
            <div class="top-bar-right">
<div id="player-event-timers"></div>
                <div id="zoom-controls">
                    <button id="zoom-out-btn" class="zoom-button">-</button>
                    <button id="zoom-in-btn" class="zoom-button">+</button>
                </div>
                <button id="logout-button">로그아웃</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="game-container">
            <div id="world-boss-container" class="world-boss-panel" style="display: none; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                <div class="character-header">
                    <h2 id="world-boss-name"></h2>
                    <button id="attack-target-toggle-btn" class="explore">월드 보스 공격</button>
                </div>
                <div class="hp-bar">
                    <div id="world-boss-hp-bar" class="hp-bar-inner"></div>
                    <div id="world-boss-hp-text" class="hp-bar-text"></div>
                </div>
                <div id="world-boss-contribution"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="main-content-wrapper">
                <div class="left-sector">
                    <div class="character-panel player-panel">
                        <div class="character-header">
                           <h2>
    플레이어
    <div id="artifact-sockets-header"></div>
    <span id="player-max-level-display" style="font-size: 0.8em; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: normal;"></span>
</h2>
 <div class="resource-display">💰 <span id="gold">0</span></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hp-bar">
                            <div class="hp-bar-inner" id="player-hp-bar"></div>
                            <div class="hp-bar-text" id="player-hp-text"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-info-combined">
                            <div class="stat-row" data-stat-row="hp"><span class="stat-name">❤️ 총 체력</span>
		<span class="stat-value" id="total-hp"></span>
		<div class="button-group">
		    <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="hp" data-amount="1">+1</button>
                            <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="hp" data-amount="10">+10</button>
                            <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="hp" data-amount="100">+100</button>
                            <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="hp" data-amount="1000">+1K</button>
                            <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="hp" data-amount="MAX">MAX</button>
	</div>

</div>
                            <div class="stat-row" data-stat-row="attack"><span class="stat-name">⚔️ 총 공격력</span>
<span class="stat-value" id="total-attack"></span>
<div class="button-group">

                            <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="attack" data-amount="1">+1</button>
                            <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="attack" data-amount="10">+10</button>
                            <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="attack" data-amount="100">+100</button>
                            <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="attack" data-amount="1000">+1K</button>
                            <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="attack" data-amount="MAX">MAX</button>
	
</div>
</div>
                            <div class="stat-row" data-stat-row="defense">
<span class="stat-name">🛡️ 총 방어력</span>
<span class="stat-value" id="total-defense"></span>
<div class="button-group">
  <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="defense" data-amount="1">+1</button>
                            <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="defense" data-amount="10">+10</button>
                            <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="defense" data-amount="100">+100</button>
                            <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="defense" data-amount="1000">+1K</button>
                            <button class="upgrade-btn" data-stat="defense" data-amount="MAX">MAX</button>
		
		</div>
	</div>
                            <hr style="grid-column: 1 / -1; border-color: var(--border-color); margin: 5px 0;">
                            <div id="special-stats-grid" class="stat-info-monster" style="grid-column: 1 / -1; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px 15px;">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="player-buffs-container"></div>
                        <div class="equipment-section">
                            <div class="equipment-slots">
                                <div class="slot" id="weapon-slot" data-slot="weapon"></div>
                                <div class="slot" id="armor-slot" data-slot="armor"></div>
                                <div class="slot" id="pet-slot" data-slot="pet"></div>
                                <div class="slot" id="necklace-slot" data-slot="necklace"></div>
                                <div class="slot" id="earring-slot" data-slot="earring"></div>
                                <div class="slot" id="wristwatch-slot" data-slot="wristwatch"></div>
                            </div>
<div id="set-effect-display" class="set-effect-container"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="character-panel monster-panel">
                        <div class="character-header">
                            <div class="monster-header-controls">
                                <h2><span id="monster-level"></span></h2>
<button id="leave-raid-btn" class="action-btn sell-btn" style="display: none;">등반 복귀</button>
<div id="floor-controls" style="display: none;">
    <button id="personal-raid-btn" class="action-btn" style="background-color: #c0392b;">개인 레이드</button> <button id="safe-zone-btn" class="action-btn sell-btn">안전지대 복귀</button>
    <button id="frontline-btn" class="action-btn list-auction-btn">최전선 복귀</button>
</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hp-bar">
                            <div class="hp-bar-inner" id="monster-hp-bar"></div>
                            <div class="hp-bar-text" id="monster-hp-text"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hp-bar" id="monster-barrier-container" style="display: none; margin-top: 5px;">
                            <div class="hp-bar-inner" id="monster-barrier-bar" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #af52de, #c774e8);"></div>
                            <div class="hp-bar-text" id="monster-barrier-text"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-info-monster">
                            <div class="stat-row-monster"><span>❤️ 총 체력</span><span id="monster-hp-total"></span></div>
                            <div class="stat-row-monster"><span>⚔️ 공격력</span><span id="monster-attack"></span></div>
                            <div class="stat-row-monster"><span>🛡️ 방어력</span><span id="monster-defense"></span></div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="monster-ability-icons" style="display: none; justify-content: center; gap: 15px; font-size: 1.5em; margin-top: 10px;">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <main class="management-panel right-sector">
                    <div class="tabs">
                        <button class="tab-button active" data-tab="weapon-inventory-tab">무기</button>
                        <button class="tab-button" data-tab="armor-inventory-tab">방어구</button>
                        <button class="tab-button" data-tab="accessory-inventory-tab">액세서리</button>
                        <button class="tab-button" data-tab="item-inventory-tab">아이템</button>
                        <button class="tab-button" data-tab="pet-inventory-tab">펫</button>
                        <button class="tab-button" data-tab="incubator-tab">부화기</button>
                        <button class="tab-button" data-tab="enhancement-tab">대장간</button>
                        <button class="tab-button" data-tab="rift-enchant-tab">균열 마법부여</button>
                        <button class="tab-button" data-tab="fusion-tab">융합</button>
                        <button class="tab-button" data-tab="log-tab">로그</button>
                        <button class="tab-button" data-tab="chat-tab">채팅</button>
<button class="tab-button" data-tab="research-tab">연구소</button>
<button class="tab-button" data-tab="scroll-tab">주문서</button>
<button class="tab-button" data-tab="spirit-tab">정령</button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tab-content active" id="weapon-inventory-tab">
                        <div class="inventory-header"><p class="inventory-tip">아이템을 드래그하여 장착하고, 클릭하여 상세 정보를 확인하세요.</p></div>
                        <div class="inventory-container">
                            <div id="weapon-inventory" class="inventory-grid"></div>
                            <div id="weapon-interaction-panel" class="interaction-panel"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tab-content" id="armor-inventory-tab">
                        <div class="inventory-header"><p class="inventory-tip">아이템을 드래그하여 장착하고, 클릭하여 상세 정보를 확인하세요.</p></div>
                        <div id="armor-inventory" class="inventory-grid"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tab-content" id="accessory-inventory-tab">
                        <div class="inventory-header"><p class="inventory-tip">액세서리를 드래그하여 장착하고, 클릭하여 상세 정보를 확인하세요.</p></div>
                        <div id="accessory-inventory" class="inventory-grid"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tab-content" id="item-inventory-tab">
                        <div class="inventory-header"><p class="inventory-tip">아이템을 클릭하여 사용하거나 부화기에 넣을 수 있습니다.</p></div>
                        <div id="item-inventory" class="inventory-grid"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tab-content" id="pet-inventory-tab">
                        <div class="inventory-header"><p class="inventory-tip">펫을 드래그하여 장착하고, 클릭하여 거래소에 등록할 수 있습니다.</p></div>
                        <div id="pet-inventory" class="inventory-grid"></div>
                    </div>
<div class="tab-content" id="incubator-tab">
    <div id="incubator-grid-container">
        </div>
</div>

                    <div class="tab-content" id="enhancement-tab">
                        <div class="enhancement-anvil">
                            <div class="enhancement-slot-wrapper">
                                <div class="enhancement-slot" id="enhancement-slot">강화할 아이템을 인벤토리에서 선택하세요</div>
                                <div class="enhancement-animation" id="enhancement-animation"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="enhancement-details">
                                <div id="enhancement-before"></div>
                                <div class="arrow">➔</div>
                                <div id="enhancement-after"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="enhancement-info" id="enhancement-info"></div>
                            <div class="enhancement-checkboxes-wrapper">
                                <div class="checkbox-wrapper">
                                    <input type="checkbox" id="use-prevention-ticket" disabled>
                                    <label for="use-prevention-ticket">파괴 방지권 사용</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="checkbox-wrapper">
                                    <input type="checkbox" id="use-hammer-ticket" disabled>
                                    <label for="use-hammer-ticket">헤파이토스의 망치 사용 (+15%p)</label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <button class="enhance-execute-btn" id="enhance-button" disabled>강 화</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tab-content" id="rift-enchant-tab">
                        <div class="enhancement-anvil">
                            <div class="enhancement-slot-wrapper">
                                <div class="enhancement-slot" id="rift-enchant-slot">마법을 부여할 장비를 선택하세요 (무기/방어구)</div>
                            </div>
                            <div id="rift-enchant-options" class="rift-options-container">
                            </div>
                            <div id="rift-enchant-cost" class="enhancement-info"></div>
                            <button class="enhance-execute-btn" id="rift-enchant-execute-btn" disabled>마 법 부 여</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tab-content" id="fusion-tab">
                        <div id="fusion-container">
                            <div id="fusion-process-ui">
                                <div class="fusion-slot-wrapper">
                                    <div class="fusion-slot" id="fusion-slot-1" data-slot-index="1">
                                        <span class="fusion-slot-placeholder">재료1 (에픽 펫)</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="fusion-pet-info" id="fusion-pet-info-1"></div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="fusion-indicator">+</div>
                                <div class="fusion-slot-wrapper">
                                    <div class="fusion-slot" id="fusion-slot-2" data-slot-index="2">
                                        <span class="fusion-slot-placeholder">재료2 (에픽 펫)</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="fusion-pet-info" id="fusion-pet-info-2"></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div id="fusion-timer-ui" style="display: none;">
                                <div class="fusion-result-preview">
                                    <img src="/image/egg_mythic.png" alt="융합 중">
                                </div>
                                <h3>융합 진행 중...</h3>
                                <div id="fusion-timer">12:00:00</div>
                                <p>완료 시 새로운 펫이 펫 인벤토리로 지급됩니다.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="fusion-controls">
                                <p id="fusion-rules">
                                    규칙: 서로 다른 속성(물, 불, 바람)의 에픽 펫 2마리를 재료로 사용합니다.<br>
                                    비용: <span class="gold-text">100,000,000 G</span>
                                </p>
                                <button id="fusion-start-button" class="enhance-execute-btn" disabled>융합 시작</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="tab-content" id="log-tab"><ul id="game-log"></ul></div>
                    <div class="tab-content" id="chat-tab">
                        <ul id="chat-messages"></ul>
                        <form id="chat-form">
                            <input id="chat-input" autocomplete="off" placeholder="메시지를 입력하세요"/>
                            <button type="submit">전송</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>

<div class="tab-content" id="account-storage-tab">
    <p class="inventory-tip">동일 카카오 계정만 사용가능합니다</p>
    <div id="account-storage-grid" class="inventory-grid"></div>
</div>

<div class="tab-content" id="research-tab">
                        </div>

<div class="tab-content" id="spirit-tab">
    <div class="inventory-header">
        <p class="inventory-tip">정령은 소지하고만 있어도 오프라인 보너스를 제공합니다. (가장 높은 등급 하나만 적용)</p>
    </div>
    <div id="spirit-inventory" class="inventory-grid"></div>
</div>

<div class="tab-content" id="scroll-tab">
    <div id="scroll-enhancement-container" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 100%; gap: 15px; padding: 15px;">
        
      <div id="scroll-target-sector" style="flex: 1; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; min-height: 200px;">
    <div id="scroll-target-placeholder" style="text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted);">
        강화할 장착 아이템을 클릭하세요.
    </div>
    <div id="scroll-target-item-display" style="display: none; width: 100%; max-width: 500px;">
        <div id="scroll-target-slot-container">
<div id="scroll-target-item-image" class="enhancement-slot"></div>
            <div id="scroll-target-item-details">
                <h3 id="scroll-item-name"></h3>
                <div id="scroll-item-stats-list">
                    </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <button id="scroll-execute-btn" class="enhance-execute-btn" style="width: 80%; margin-top: 20px; display: none;"></button>
    <div id="scroll-enhancement-animation" class="enhancement-animation"></div>
</div>

        <div id="scroll-material-sector" style="flex: 1.2; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px;">
            <h4 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--text-muted);">보유 주문서 및 아이템</h4>
            <div id="scroll-material-grid" class="inventory-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(130px, 1fr));">
                </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

                </main>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="auction-modal" class="modal-overlay" style="display: none;">
        <div class="modal-content auction-modal-content">
            <span class="close-button">&times;</span>
            <h2>⚖️ 거래소</h2>
            
            <div class="auction-controls">
                <input type="text" id="auction-search-input" placeholder="아이템 이름으로 검색...">
                <select id="auction-grade-filter">
                    <option value="전체">전체 등급</option>
                    <option value="Common">Common</option>
                    <option value="Rare">Rare</option>
                    <option value="Legendary">Legendary</option>
                    <option value="Epic">Epic</option>
                    <option value="Mystic">Mystic</option>
                    <option value="Primal">Primal</option>
                </select>
                <button id="auction-refresh-btn" class="action-btn">새로고침</button>
            </div>

            <div id="auction-container">
                <div class="auction-list-panel">
                    <div id="auction-grouped-grid" class="inventory-grid"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="auction-detail-panel">
                    <div id="auction-detail-list">
                        <p class="inventory-tip" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 50px;">왼쪽에서 아이템을 선택하세요.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="ranking-modal" class="modal-overlay" style="display: none;">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close-button">&times;</span>
            <h2>🏆 무한의 탑 명예의 전당</h2>
            <ul id="ranking-list"></ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="loot-record-modal" class="modal-overlay" style="display: none;">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close-button">&times;</span>
            <h2>💎 서버 최고 득템 기록</h2>
            <div id="loot-record-display"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="enhancement-record-modal" class="modal-overlay" style="display: none;">
        <div class="modal-content">
